### 🚀 About Me

<div align="center">
  <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/vgO6x0XIfjB4A4h7hD/giphy.gif" width="120" align="right" style="margin-left: 20px;">
</div>

- 🎓 I'm an **Energy Science & Engineering** student at **IIT Bombay** (2024 - 2028).
- 🔭 I’m currently working on **Energy Analytics**, **Solar & Wind Power Forecasting**, and **Deep Learning (CNN-LSTM)**.
- 🌱 I’m constantly exploring deeper into **Microgrid Design**, **Robotics/UAVs**, and **Finance/Investment Strategies**.
- 💬 Ask me about **Python, PyTorch, Time-Series Forecasting, and Energy Systems**.
- 📫 How to reach me: Drop an email at **pritamnew18@gmail.com** or connect on LinkedIn/GitHub!
- ⚡ Fun fact: I organize events for Asia's Largest College Cultural Festival (**Mood Indigo**) managing over 25,000+ participants!

